data.meta_description: Valencia University Information, Campus and History: Located in Valencia, Spain, the University of Valencia is one of the largest and oldest universities in Spain. It was founded on 30 April 1499, as passed by the municipal magistrates of Valencia at the request of James I the Conqueror and authorization of Pope Innocent IV.
